===Noun===
'''Durational pattern'''

#In [[music]], '''durational patterns''' are the foreground details projected against a background [[metric structure]]. They may be [[rhythmic unit]]s or [[rhythmic gesture]]s. (DeLone et. al. (Eds.), 1975, chap. 3)

